<td class="relatedlinkbox" width="147"><font size="1"><strong>"For me science isn't a subject, it's a perspective. There are fascinating scientific aspects to everything from ancient history to the latest gadgets, outer space to interior decorating; and each week on The Material World we try to reflect the excitement, ideas, uncertainties, collisions and collaborations as science continues its never-ending voyage into the unknown".
<br><br>
Quentin Cooper</strong></font></td>
